title: Dak Prescott, Baker Mayfield, moving on, and the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Baker Mayfield, moving on, and the Blazing 5
description:
Colin talks about the doubters of Dallas Cowboys QB Dak Prescott, what worries him about Cleveland Browns QB Baker Mayfield, teams that are happy about moving on from certain players, and his Blazing 5 picks. Guests include Peter Schrager, Greg Jennings, Rich Ohrnberger, and Jason McIntyre.
